Class ChangePoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unisa.sesa.repominer.dbscan.ChangePoint

  • public class ChangePoint
extends java.lang.Object
    An implementation of Change for points with integer coordinates A single ChangePoint has two instance variables, a Change instance and an integer coordinate

    repominerEvo Team
